'''''La Negrada izwi''''' mpuzamahanga nka '''Black Mexicans,'''  yasohotse  2018 ni filime yo muri [[Megizike|Mexique]] iyoborwa na Jorge Pérez Solano afatanyije na   César Gutiérrez Miranda na  Tirisia Cine. <ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/co/film990099.html</ref> <ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/an-interview-with-the-filmmaker-behind-la-negrada-the-first-feature-film-starring-an-all-afro-mexican-cast/</ref> <ref>https://www.tfiny.org/films/detail/la_negrada</ref> <ref>http://mujeresenmedio.org/la-negrada-anti-blackness-under-the-guise-of-visibility/</ref> Niyo filime ya mbere yo muri Mexique yimpimbano hamwe hagati ya Africa na Mexico bose bakinnye muri Mexico. Filime yafatiwe mu mijyi mito no muri Costa Chica, Oaxaca. <ref name="remezcla">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://remezcla.com/film/trailer-la-negrada-afro-mexican/ "<span class="cs1-kern-left">'</span>La Negrada' Is Mexico's First-Ever Fiction Film to Have an All-Black Cast"]. remezcla<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 18 Kanama 2018 muri [[Amerika]]. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nyuma iza gutsindira igihembo cyiza cya Sinema mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Guadalajara 2018. <ref name="remezcla">https://remezcla.com/film/trailer-la-negrada-afro-mexican/</ref>

== Kwerekanwa mpuzamahanga ==

* Iserukiramuco rya Filime nyafurika rya Diaspora, Amerika - 18 Kanama 2018
* Centro Cultural de España, Uruguay - 1 Nyakanga 2019
* Iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Hola Mexico, Amerika - 4 Kamena 2020

